==================================================================================

template: no_access
var: user, target, group, run_as, directory

TEAM list, read, write, rename, delete, chmod, chown file

run_as: <run_as>

name: <template> list root
$ show_dir /teams
drwxr-xr-x. root root /teams

name: <template> <user> list <directory>
$ show_dir <directory>
drwxrws--T. <target>-admin <target> <directory>

name: <template> <user> list <target> files in <directory>
$ ls -1 <directory>
!!
ls: cannot open directory '<directory>': Permission denied

name: <template> <user> write <target> files in <directory>
$ echo "surpise!" ><directory>/<target>.txt
exit_code: ignore_stderr

name: <template> <user> list <target> files in <directory>
$ mv <directory> <directory>.2
!!
mv: cannot move '<directory>' to '<directory>.2': Permission denied

name: <template> <user> chmod  <target> <directory>
$ chmod 777 <directory>
!!
chmod: changing permissions of '<directory>': Operation not permitted

name: <template> <user> chown <target> <directory>
$ chown <user>:<group>  <directory>
!!
chown: changing ownership of '<directory>': Operation not permitted

end_template: no_access

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

